---
import '../styles/style.css'
import Navbar from '../components/Navbar.astro'
import '@fontsource/barlow'
import '@fontsource/barlow/600.css'
import '@fontsource/barlow/700.css'
import '@fontsource/barlow/800.css'
import '@fontsource/barlow/900.css'
---

<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>JoyCat</title>
</head>

<body>
    <Navbar />
    <header class="hero">
        <div class="left-container">
            <h1 class="title">Professional, Loving and Reliable Cat Care When You Can't be There</h1>
            <p class="description grayText">Di Joy Cat, kami berkomitmen untuk memberikan perawatan terbaik bagi kucing
                kesayangan Anda. Kami menawarkan berbagai layanan yang dirancang khusus untuk memastikan kesehatan dan
                kebahagiaan kucing Anda. Dari klinik kucing hingga daycare dan grooming, serta program adopsi, Joy Cat
                adalah pilihan tepat bagi para pemilik kucing yang peduli.</p>

            <img src="img/CatPaw.svg" alt="paw">
        </div>

        <div class="right-container">
            <div class="cats">
                <img class="cat1" src="img/cat3.jpg" alt="cat1">
                <img class="cat2" src="img/cat1.jpg" alt="cat2">
                <img class="cat3" src="img/cat2.jpg" alt="cat3">
            </div>
        </div>
    </header>

    <main>
        <h1>Our Services</h1>
        <div class="card">
            <!-- CRAD ONE -->
            <div class="card1">
                <img class="header" src="img/card1.jpeg" alt="card1">

                <div class="bio">
                    <h1 class="name">Klinik Kucing</h1>
                    <p class="description">Tim dokter hewan kami yang berpengalaman siap memberikan perawatan medis
                        terbaik untuk kucing Anda. Kami menyediakan layanan vaksinasi, pemeriksaan rutin, pengobatan
                        penyakit, dan konsultasi kesehatan.</p>

                    <button>Cek Dokter</button>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- CARD TWO -->
            <div class="card2">
                <img class="header" src="img/card2.webp" alt="card2">

                <div class="bio">
                    <h1 class="name">Daycare & Grooming</h1>
                    <p class="description">Butuh tempat yang aman dan nyaman untuk menitipkan kucing Anda saat Anda
                        sibuk? Daycare kami adalah solusinya. Selain itu, layanan grooming kami akan membuat kucing Anda
                        tetap bersih dan cantik.</p>

                    <button>Lihat Paket</button>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- CARD THREE -->
            <div class="card3">
                <img class="header" src="img/card3.jpg" alt="card3">

                <div class="bio">
                    <h1 class="name">Adopsi Kucing</h1>
                    <p class="description">Bantu kami menemukan rumah baru yang penuh cinta untuk kucing-kucing yang
                        membutuhkan. Lihat kucing-kucing yang siap diadopsi dan jadilah bagian dari cerita bahagia
                        mereka.</p>

                    <button>Cek Kucing</button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>

    <article class="map">
        <div class="JamCard">
            <p class="JamCardText">Opening Hours</p>
            <div class="infoCard">
                <div class="infoo">
                    <p class="bluText">Weekdays</p>
                    <p class="time">08.00-17.00</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="infoCard">
                <div class="infoo">
                    <p class="bluText">Weekend</p>
                    <p class="time">07.00-19.00</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <hr>

            <p class="JamCardText">Kontak Cepat</p>
            <div class="infoCard">
                <div class="infoo">
                    <p class="bluText">Whatsapp</p>
                    <p class="time">0812-1234-5678</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="cardMap">
            <p class="cardMapText">Alamat Kami</span></p>
            <div class="infoContainer">
                <div class="info">
                    <p class="grayTexyInfo">Jl. Radar Auri No.32d, Cisalak Ps., Kec. Cimanggis, Kota Depok, Jawa Barat
                        16452</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <iframe
                src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m14!1m8!1m3!1d15860.663436893967!2d106.8679048!3d-6.3725769!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x2e69edee0a2b7f05%3A0x95ab16f97f8f308a!2sMoreTHAN%20Veterinary%20Clinic!5e0!3m2!1sen!2sid!4v1717069595245!5m2!1sen!2sid"
                width="600" height="450" style="border:0;" allowfullscreen="" loading="lazy"
                referrerpolicy="no-referrer-when-downgrade"></iframe>
        </div>
    </article>

    <section>
        <h1>Testimonials</h1>
        <div class="CommentCard">
            <div class="CardOne">
                <img class="quote" src="img/quote.svg" alt="">
                <p>It was my second time there. I believe my cat, Dusty had a good time there. Had a major timming and
                    royal splash spa. The fur is still smooth after 2 weeks. They took great care of Dusty knowing that
                    she is pregnant. Recommended!</p>
                <li>Amelia Rose</li>
            </div>

            <div class="CardTwo">
                <img class="quote" src="img/quote.svg" alt="">
                <p>Clean and nice for the cats. Grooming package is good too. We chose a special package for our catüê±,
                    Molly. Today we sent 6 cats for boarding. Love JoyCat service!</p>
                <li>Niki Jasmine</li>
            </div>

            <div class="CardThree">
                <img class="quote" src="img/quote.svg" alt="">
                <p>Sent Casper for grooming and chose to try aromatic salt bath. She enjoyed the session and seems
                    calmer and approachable compared to before üòç. The place is well kept and adhere to Covid 19 SOP.
                    Really recommended!</p>
                <li>Hannah Isma</li>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <footer>
        <div class="containerFooter">
            <img src="img/logo-light.svg" alt="">
            <div class="footerTextOne">
                <ul class="textOne">
                    <li>Main Links</li>
                    <li>Home</li>
                    <li>Klinik</li>
                    <li>Daycare & Grooming</li>
                    <li>Adopsi</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="footerTextTwo">
                <ul class="textTwo">
                    <li>Contacts</li>
                    <li>0812-3456-78910</li>
                    <li>admin@joycat.com</li>
                    <li>Jl. Radar Auri No.32d, Cisalak <br> Ps., Kec. Cimanggis, Kota <br> Depok, Jawa
                        Barat 16452</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="footerTextThree">
                <ul class="textThree">
                    <li>Follow us for updates</li>
                </ul>
                <div class="footerIcon">
                    <img src="img/Icon-YT.svg" alt="">
                    <img src="img/Icon-TT.svg" alt="">
                    <img src="img/Icon-IG.svg" alt="">
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </footer>
    <hr class="footerHr">
    <footer>
